title: BBC Life In Cold Blood 3of5 Dragons Of The Dry XviD AC3
description:
Part 3 - Dragons Of The Dry 
Enter the world of the lizard: from the chameleons, masters of the aboreal life to geckos tapping a code to plant-hopper insects and baby pygmy blue-tongued skinks huddling in their burrows long after birth. In the deserts are found some of the most bizarre lizards: baby Bushveld lizards mimicking acid-squirting beetles; the well-armoured and bizarrely spiky; thorny devils and the lizard kings - the Australian monitors - fast, intelligent and efficient hunters.
